DE_GRISTMILL

Created By: Wheel-Knee
Contact: wheelknee@gmail.com
Release Date: April 08/2005
Capacity: 48

This map was inspired by a mill in Bucks Co. Pennsylvania that was built in 1927.

OBJECTIVE

This mill is an important rail supply depot. Terrorists must disable this mill's ability to produce and move goods. Bomb the mill components inside, or the crane outside.
